data.description: This Captivating, ever charming 3 bedrooms and 2 baths open plan style house is NOW available for your showing. Upgraded Kitchen wit beautiful kitchen counters, custom built backsplash, standstill large sink, good grade floors, and breakfast middle island and cabinets. Upgraded bathroom with double vanity now yours for the taking. The dining room/living area are just off the kitchen and features a Designed fireplace and the lovely views of landscaped backyard and pool area . Just off the kitchen, you can access the backyard patio and barbecue area overlooking the pool. Good size spacious 3 bedrooms with large closets. First bedroom is a master bedroom with large closet, shower tub and nice double vanity sink. Good size bedrooms , plenty of storage area and cabinets through out the hallway to the bedrooms and good size bathroom with tub .Beautiful layout and appealing landscape with a large pool and new cocrete patio area! Don't mess on this opportunity and schedule your appointment now
